{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Screen Wake Lock API",
    "url": "https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "Screen Wake Lock permission revocation algorithm",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-screen-wake-lock-permission-revocation-algorithm",
      "html": "The <code>\"screen-wake-lock\"</code> <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-powerful-feature\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-powerful-feature-2\">powerful feature</a> defines a <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-permission-revocation-algorithm\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-permission-revocation-algorithm-for-powerful-feature-1\">permission revocation algorithm</a>. To invoke the <dfn id=\"dfn-screen-wake-lock-permission-revocation-algorithm\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\">Screen\n          Wake Lock permission revocation algorithm</dfn>, run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Let <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#current-global-object\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-current-global-object-1\">current global object</a>'s\n          <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-associated-document-1\">associated Document</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var>lockList</var> be\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-1\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[\"<code>screen</code>\"]."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-for-each-for-list-1\">For each</a> <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> in <var>lockList</var>:",
          "rationale": "run",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Run <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-a-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-a-wake-lock-1\">release a wake lock</a> with <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>, <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>, and\n              \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocktype-screen\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocktype-screen-1\"><code>screen</code></a>\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <code>request(<var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>)</code> method steps are:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Let <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-this-1\">this</a>'s <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-relevant-global-object-1\">relevant global object</a>'s <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-associated-document-2\">associated Document</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-fully-active-for-document-1\">fully active</a>, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-promise-rejected-with-1\">a promise rejected with</a> with a \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-1\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\" <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-1\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/iframe-embed-object.html#allowed-to-use\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-allowed-to-use-1\">allowed to use</a> the <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions-policy-1/#policy-controlled-feature\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-policy-controlled-feature-2\">policy-controlled feature</a> named \"<code>screen-wake-lock</code>\", return <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-promise-rejected-with-2\">a promise rejected with</a> a \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-2\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\" <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-2\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If\n          the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-user-agent\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-2\">user agent</a> <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-deny-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-deny-wake-lock-1\">denies the wake lock</a> of this <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var> for\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-promise-rejected-with-3\">a promise rejected with</a> a\n          \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-3\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\" <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-3\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>'s <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#visibility-state\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-visibility-state-for-document-1\">visibility state</a> is \"<code>hidden</code>\", return <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-promise-rejected-with-4\">a promise rejected with</a> \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-4\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\" <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-4\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-new-promise\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-new-promise-1\">a new promise</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Run the following steps <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#in-parallel\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-in-parallel-1\">in parallel</a>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Let <var data-type=\"PermissionState\">state</var> be the result of <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-request-permission-to-use\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-requesting-permission-to-use-1\">requesting\n              permission to use</a> \"<code>screen-wake-lock</code>\"."
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var data-type=\"PermissionState\">state</var> is\n              \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"enum-value\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-denied\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-denied-for-permissionstate-1\"><code>denied</code></a>\", then:",
              "rationale": "queue",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-queue-a-global-task-1\">Queue a global task</a> on the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-screen-wake-lock-task-source\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-screen-wake-lock-task-source-1\">screen wake lock task\n                    source</a> given <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>'s <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-relevant-global-object-2\">relevant global object</a>\n                    to reject <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var> with a \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-5\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\"\n                    <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-5\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Abort these steps."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-queue-a-global-task-2\">Queue a global task</a> on the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-screen-wake-lock-task-source\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-screen-wake-lock-task-source-2\">screen wake lock task\n                source</a> given <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>'s <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-relevant-global-object-3\">relevant global object</a> to\n                run these steps:",
              "rationale": "if",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "If <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-fully-active-for-document-2\">fully active</a>, then:",
                  "rationale": "reject",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "html": "Reject <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var> with a \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-6\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\"\n                      <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-6\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
                    },
                    {
                      "html": "Abort these steps."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "html": "If <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>'s <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#visibility-state\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-visibility-state-for-document-2\">visibility state</a> is\n                  \"<code>hidden</code>\", then:",
                  "rationale": "reject",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "html": "Reject <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var> with a \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-type=\"exception\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-notallowederror-exception-7\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></a>\"\n                      <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"DOMException\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-domexception-interface-7\"><code>DOMException</code></a>."
                    },
                    {
                      "html": "Abort these steps."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "html": "If <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-2\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[\"<code>screen</code>\"]\n                  <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-is-empty\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-is-empty-for-list-1\">is empty</a>, then invoke the following steps <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#in-parallel\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-in-parallel-2\">in\n                  parallel</a>:",
                  "rationale": "invoke",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "html": "Invoke <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-acquire-a-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-acquire-a-wake-lock-1\">acquire a wake lock</a> with\n                      \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocktype-screen\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocktype-screen-2\"><code>screen</code></a>\"."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "html": "Let <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"WakeLockSentinel\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocksentinel\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocksentinel-3\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a>\n                  object with its <a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocksentinel-type\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocksentinel-type-1\"><code>type</code></a> attribute set to\n                  <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-append\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-append-for-list-1\">Append</a> <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> to\n                  <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-3\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[\"<code>screen</code>\"]."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Resolve <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var> with <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <var data-type=\"Promise\">promise</var>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"release()\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocksentinel-release\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocksentinel-release-2\"><code>release</code></a><code>()</code> method steps are:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-this-4\">this</a>'s <a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[Released]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-released\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-released-2\"><code>[[Released]]</code></a> is <code>false</code>,\n          then run <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-a-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-a-wake-lock-2\">release a wake lock</a> with <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> set\n          to <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-this-5\">this</a> and <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var> set to the value of\n          <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-this-6\">this</a>'s <a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocksentinel-type\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocksentinel-type-4\"><code>type</code></a> attribute."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-resolved-with\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-a-promise-resolved-with-1\">a promise resolved with</a> <code>undefined</code>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "When a <a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"Document\" data-type=\"interface\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-document-interface-3\"><code>Document</code></a> <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var> becomes no longer\n          <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-fully-active-for-document-3\">fully active</a>, the user agent must run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-for-each-for-list-2\">For each</a> <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> in\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-5\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[\"<code>screen</code>\"]:",
          "rationale": "run",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Run <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-a-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-a-wake-lock-5\">release a wake lock</a> with <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>, <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>, and\n              \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocktype-screen\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocktype-screen-4\"><code>screen</code></a>\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "This specification defines the following <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#page-visibility-change-steps\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-page-visibility-change-steps-1\">page visibility change steps</a> with <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#visibility-state\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-visibility-state-for-document-3\">visibility state</a> <var>state</var> and\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>state</var> is not \"<code>hidden</code>\", abort these steps."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-for-each-for-list-3\">For each</a> <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> in\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-6\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[\"<code>screen</code>\"]:",
          "rationale": "run",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Run <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-a-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-a-wake-lock-6\">release a wake lock</a> with <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>, <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>, and\n              \"<a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dom-wakelocktype-screen\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-wakelocktype-screen-5\"><code>screen</code></a>\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "acquire a wake lock",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-acquire-a-wake-lock",
      "html": "To <dfn id=\"dfn-acquire-a-wake-lock\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\">acquire a wake lock</dfn> for a given <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>,\n          run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If the wake lock for type <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var> is not <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-applicable-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-applicable-wake-lock-2\">applicable</a>, abort\n          these steps."
        },
        {
          "html": "Ask the underlying operating system to <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-acquire-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-acquire-wake-lock-1\">acquire the wake\n          lock</a> of type <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "release a wake lock",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-a-wake-lock",
      "html": "To <dfn id=\"dfn-release-a-wake-lock\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\">release a wake lock</dfn> for a given <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>,\n          <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>, and <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>, run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-7\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[<var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>] does not\n          contain <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>, abort these steps."
        },
        {
          "html": "Remove <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var> from\n          <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-8\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[<var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>]."
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var data-type=\"Document\">document</var>.<a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[ActiveLocks]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-activelocks\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-activelocks-9\"><code>[[ActiveLocks]]</code></a>[<var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var>] <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-is-empty\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-is-empty-for-list-2\">is empty</a>, then run the following steps <a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#in-parallel\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-in-parallel-3\">in parallel</a>:",
          "rationale": "ask",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Ask the underlying operating system to <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release-wake-lock\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-wake-lock-1\">release the wake\n              lock</a> of type <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var> and let <var data-type=\"boolean\">success</var> be <code>true</code> if\n              the operation succeeded, or else <code>false</code>."
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var data-type=\"boolean\">success</var> is <code>true</code> and <var data-type=\"WakeLockType\">type</var> is <code>\"screen\"</code> run the\n              following:",
              "rationale": "reset",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "Reset the platform-specific inactivity timer after which\n                  the screen is actually turned off."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>'s <a data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-lt=\"[[Released]]\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-released\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-released-3\"><code>[[Released]]</code></a> to <code>true</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire\" id=\"ref-for-index-term-fire-an-event-1\">Fire an event</a> named \"<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-wake-lock/#dfn-release\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-release-2\"><code><code>release</code></code></a>\" at <var data-type=\"WakeLockSentinel\">lock</var>."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}